data.description: Here is your chance to own 10 acres of Texas with easy access and close to town! This beautiful lot is located directly off of Hwy 173 between Devine and Jourdanton in the lovely Sendero Crossing subdivision. HOA is in place to protect your investment, with very light restrictions and low annual dues. Mesquite trees and native brush provide perfect hunting conditions, or clear it out for livestock and/or to build your dream home!
